    <lb n="20"/><supplied reason="lost">μ</supplied>ου καὶ Σε<supplied reason="lost">ρηνί</supplied>λλαν καὶ το<supplied reason="lost">ὺς</supplied> φίλους μο<supplied reason="lost">υ</supplied>. 

    <lb n="21"/>ἔπεμψά σο<supplied reason="lost">ι εἰ</supplied>κόνιν μ<supplied reason="lost">ου</supplied> διὰ Εὐκτή


    <lb n="22" type="worddiv"/>μονος.  <app type="BL"><lem resp="cf. 8.27">ἔσ<supplied reason="lost">τ</supplied><unclear>ι</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ν</supplied></lem><rdg>ἔσ<supplied reason="lost">τ</supplied>ι <supplied reason="lost">δέ</supplied></rdg></app> μου ὄνομα Ἀντῶνις Μά

    <lb n="23" type="worddiv"/>ξιμος. ἐρρῶσθαί σε εὔχομαι. 

    <lb n="24"/><expan>κεντυρί<ex>α</ex></expan> Ἀθηνονίκη. 
